      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"غَبْنُ اَلْمُسْتَرْسِلِ سُحْتٌ وَ غَبْنُ اَلْمُؤْمِنِ حَرَامٌ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3982 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said: \"Defrauding the one who entrusts you is unlawful gain, and defrauding a believer is forbidden.\""
        ]
